      "date": "2011-09-10 12:49:55.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/7bf607ba-dba9-11e0-8d02-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  1 tests failed: sanityn.",
