        "email": "fan.yong@intel.com",
        "username": "nasf",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2011-09-13 13:44:38.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\nThe failure in maloo test can be fixed by adjusting sleep time in sanityn test.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
